@startuml
title app.py

package "API Components" {
    class FlaskApp {
        - Initialize the app
        - Configure logging
        - Define routes
        - Run the app
    }

    class Logger {
        - Log to file
        - Log to console
    }

    class Request {
        - Parse JSON data
        - Validate parameters
        - Process request
        - Return response
    }

    class JSONData {
        - Extract data fields
    }
}

FlaskApp --> Logger : Uses
FlaskApp --> Request : Processes
Request --> JSONData : Extracts

note right of Request
  Request handles:
  - Missing parameters
  - Repository cloning
  - Code retrieval
  - UML content generation
end note

@enduml
